msg.msgText:
A "SNMPTrapSubscriber" object can be deleted by using the "delete" option of the "imaserver" command.
SYNTAX: imaserver delete SNMPTrapSubscriber help imaserver delete SNMPTrapSubscriber Host=value
EXAMPLE: imaserver delete SNMPTrapSubscriber Host=9.3.179.144

msgExplanation.p: This message is the text of a command help.
